psalm.text:
[[Ps 68,4]]The just rejoice and exult before God; 
they are glad and rejoice.
[[Ps 68,5]]Sing to God, chant praise to his name; 
whose name is the LORD.

[[Ps 68,6]]The father of orphans and the defender of widows 
is God in his holy dwelling.
[[Ps 68,7]]God gives a home to the forsaken; 
he leads forth prisoners to prosperity.

[[Ps 68,10]]A bountiful rain you showered down, O God, upon your inheritance; 
you restored the land when it languished;
[[Ps 68,11]]your flock settled in it; 
in your goodness, O God, you provided it for the needy.
